data.description: You do not want to miss this home! Located in the Palm Cay community this home delivers a delightful two-bedroom, two-bathroom space with a one-car garage in a serene community, perfectly situated in a prime central location. With a new roof (2023) this home offers a harmonious blend of comfort and convenience, making it an ideal choice for a peaceful yet accessible lifestyle.     One of this home's highlights is the newly installed solar system (2023), promoting energy efficiency while benefiting the environment. The open, sunlit living spaces create an inviting atmosphere, with a spacious living room and an adjacent dining area, perfect for gatherings. The expansive 0.23-acre backyard, offers ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. Don't miss the chance to call this house your home, with its quiet community, eco-friendly features, and unbeatable convenience. It's a rare find in a highly desirable location.
